{"tid":621374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲男童涉非禮24歲女被捕","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T07:24:04.000Z","uid":1174,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cab3cb9fe4fcc2bd032f414005d9d6d4a72404","tid":621374,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"牛頭角彩盈邨發生非禮案，昨（7日）晚10時50分，一名24歲女子報案，指被一名「四眼仔」襲擊，要求警方協助。警員接報到場，經初步調查，相信女子在上址一樓層疑被該青年非禮，他及後逃去。案件列作非禮，交由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n至今午約3時，秀茂坪警區重案組在彩盈邨拘捕一名13歲男童，涉嫌非禮。該名男童正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"4729ff96836ca3091130565dc8a139552ee637cf","tid":621374,"uid":1174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180408/mobile/bkn-20180408165623020-0408_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180408%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180408165623020-0408_00822_001.html&d=c0cgvjwHXMmVisdxPFAbKAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6d9a7fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180408/mobile/bkn-20180408165623020-0408_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a9b791d39cf765eec75be07a318a6f17894e33c","tid":621374,"uid":169468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:18:47.000Z","msg":"究竟係襲擊定非禮?"},{"pid":"69fc3b52b1517c21404083c1a36a0630d73c293e","tid":621374,"uid":6674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"香港加1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e716b7170b5a745232eb9b5a00dbcdbbf865b5","tid":621374,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0261097f0f92f15b21509388e145459e95b99cbf","tid":621374,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"連登仔 :「所以話呢 ...」"},{"pid":"57ee320cb